          <p class="is-size-5">
            The Sari-Sari Store Inventory Manager is a web-based application designed specifically 
            for Filipino neighborhood stores (sari-sari stores). It helps store owners track products, 
            monitor stock levels, calculate inventory value, and manage their business more efficiently.
          </p>

          <h3 class="title is-4">üéØ Key Features</h3>
          <div class="columns">
