          <h3 class="title is-4">üìà Inventory Metrics</h3>
          <p>The system automatically calculates and displays:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Total Products:</strong> Number of different product types</li>
            <li><strong>Total Items:</strong> Sum of all units across all products</li>
            <li><strong>Total Value:</strong> Current worth of entire inventory (price √ó stock)</li>
            <li><strong>Low Stock Count:</strong> Products with 10 or fewer units</li>
            <li><strong>Out of Stock:</strong> Products with zero stock (need immediate reorder)</li>
            <li><strong>Category Analysis:</strong> Products, stock, and value per category</li>
          </ul>

